-what-a-relief-with-tender-single-aftertaste-and-details-of-us-tour-and-london-show-3777220">凯蒂·加文 (Katie Gavin) 正准备于 10 月 25 日发行她的首张个人专辑《What A Relief》</a> ，您可以<a href="https://katie-gavin.lnk.to/What-A-Relief" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>。她已经分享了单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/munas-katie-gavin-announces-debut-solo-album-what-a-relief-with-tender-single-aftertaste-and-details-of-us-tour-and-london-show-3777220">Aftertaste</a> ”和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/munas-katie-gavin-deals-in-being-young-and-on-bad-behaviour-on-new-solo-single-casual-drug-use-3785714">Casual Drug Use</a> ”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/muna-call-out-truly-scary-toxic-fan-behaviour-cannot-believe-this-needs-explaining-3791725">MUNA 的帖子指出“真正可怕的”有毒粉丝行为：“不敢相信这需要解释”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
